Products.Name: Qwest - Escape Qwest - Death Bubba - Indica 1G
Products.ShortDescription: Robust and full-bodied musky aroma with earthy terpenes.
Products.LongDescription: Qwests Escape Qwest (Death Bubba) is cultivated using the mineral rich soils and streams of the Pacific Northwest. A heavy indica, Death Bubba presents a robust flower structure, which yields earthy terpenes of wood and pine. With bright pistils and bulbous trichomes, Death Bubba has a familiar musk reminiscent of other BC-grown favourites.

ProductSpecifications.Value: Qwest - Escape Qwest - Death Bubba - Indica 1G

Products.Name: Qwest Reserve - Wedding Breath -  Indica 1G
Products.ShortDescription: Creamy taste with subtle spice flavours.
Products.LongDescription: Spirit Qwest (Wedding Breath, a cross between Wedding Cake and Mendo Breath) is a rare indica-dominant strain with a grape profile and a flower structure akin to the renowned Purple Haze. Qwest cannabis is small-batch grown, hand-trimmed, and top cut (to attain the densest and most robust flowers).

Products.Name: Qwest - Zest Qwest - Super Lemon Haze - Sativa 1G
Products.ShortDescription: Aromatic zesty citrus and subtly sweet flavours.
Products.LongDescription: Sativa-dominant Super Lemon Haze strain (Zest Qwest), combining favoured genetics from popular parent strains Lemon Skunk and Super Silver Haze, Super Lemon Haze has a frosty layer of kief bearing a blonde tint. Naturally lanky flowers feature signature aromatics of zesty citrus. Qwest cannabis is small-batch grown, hand-trimmed, and top cut (to attain the densest and most robust buds).

Products.Name: Qwest - Wonder Qwest - Sour Diesel - Sativa 1G
